title: [FSX/P3D] Miami_City_X P3D v4 compatible
description:
Scenery features:

Fully compatible with FSX, FSX:Steam Edition, and P3D v1 - v4.
Very large photoreal area of Miami city with autogen, including Miami Beach, Key Biscayne, Kendall, Doral, Hialeah, Opa-Locka and Golden Glades; perfect for VFR/IFR flights
Over a thousand of custom-made buildings in Miami Downtown, Miami Beach and Key Biscayne areas
Lite, up-to-date airports of KMIA, KTMB and KOPF, each with a separate Scenery Library input for an easy deactivation and an extremely FPS-friendly design
Start locations for 10 helipads (2FA0, 9FA8, 64FL, 71FL, FA76, FD00, FD23, FL83, FL93, X48), one sea plane base (X44) and one closed airport (X46) included
Basic night version

Compatibility:

This product is compatible with mesh, landclass and vector add-ons. It is also compatible with KMIA Miami Intl. Airport scenery by Latin VFR
